{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Postgres surfaced the next real issue: one generated foreign-key name exceeded PostgreSQL\u2019s 63-character identifier limit. I\u2019m shortening that self-referential composition-segment constraint in both the ORM and the first revision, then I...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_74", "text": "Postgres surfaced the next real issue: one generated foreign-key name exceeded PostgreSQL\u2019s 63-character identifier limit. I\u2019m shortening that self-referential composition-segment constraint in both the ORM and the first revision, then I\u2019ll rerun the live upgrade cycle.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 141, "prompt_index": 12, "prompt_name": "11 \u2014 PostgreSQL Schema and Database Migrations", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T22:52:46-07:00"}
